Subject: [PATCH] docs: Fix path in command to remove a system extension

Signed-off-by: Felicitas Pojtinger <felicitas@pojtinger.com>
---
diff --git a/docs/new/build.md b/docs/new/build.md
index e657c8a9dd08034ffe4118fc015c824c15fae169..1c9fffe59fca0f550f231b7d31138a8628c39d72 100644
--- a/docs/new/build.md
+++ b/docs/new/build.md
@@ -107,7 +107,7 @@
 To remove the system extension from your workstation, run the following:
 
 ```shell
-$ run0 rm /var/lib/extensions/zz-gnome-control-center.sysext.raw
+$ run0 rm /var/lib/extensions/zz-gnome-control-center.raw
 $ run0 systemd-sysext refresh
 ```
 

